Package: doShard
Type: Package
Title: Foreach Parallel Adapter for the 'shard' Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("First", "Last", email = "you@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Author: First Last [aut, cre]
Maintainer: First Last <you@example.org>
Description: Provides a foreach parallel adapter that uses the 'shard' package
    as the parallel backend. This allows users to leverage shard's deterministic,
    zero-copy parallel execution with worker supervision and memory monitoring
    through the familiar foreach interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0),
    foreach (>= 1.5.0)
Imports:
    shard,
    iterators
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
